    "summary": "A responsive, content-first design system utilizing atomic principles to support real-time feeds and multimedia interactions.",
    "description": "The visual philosophy prioritizes content legibility and interaction speed. Using a 'Clean Modern' aesthetic, the interface minimizes chrome to let user-generated content shine. The color palette uses a deep Indigo primary for trust and stability, with vibrant accents for interactions. The layout adopts a classic 3-column structure (Navigation, Feed, Widgets) optimized for desktop, collapsing to a bottom-nav single column on mobile. Optimistic UI patterns are heavily employed to mask network latency.",
