    "layout_strategy": "Responsive 3-column grid (Left Nav, Center Content, Right Widgets) collapsing to 1-column on mobile.",
    "visual_philosophy": "Clean, whitespace-heavy design that emphasizes user content over UI chrome. Uses a cool color palette to reduce eye strain during prolonged usage.",
    "information_architecture": "The application uses a flat hierarchy with a persistent side navigation on desktop and bottom navigation on mobile. The primary view is the 'Feed', with secondary views for 'Explore', 'Notifications', and 'Messages'. Contextual actions (like creating a post) are available globally via a Floating Action Button (mobile) or prominent header button (desktop).",
    "responsive_strategy": "Mobile-first approach using Tailwind CSS breakpoints. Complex components like the 'ChatWindow' transform from a floating widget on desktop to a full-screen page on mobile.",
